{"tid":1252153,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"屌 cctvb係咁播洗腦維穩新聞","createTime":"2019-06-23T00:16:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T08:51:13.000Z","uid":6181,"like":912,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"51d672d5794d0ae4c32415876b3bb4589adba205","tid":1252153,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T00:16:45.000Z","msg":"好撚恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩老係咪都睇cctvb，我睇見都好撚炆， 想一拳打爆個電視<br />\n<br />\n點解cctvb可以咁撚紅底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做新聞個班有冇撚良心，同班警犬有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係屌撚柒你cctvb，我祝你好似atv咁千秋萬世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比共狗用完即棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n擺睇cctvb，我依加完全唔撚睇，平時行過電視都會自動mute左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位手足都擺睇cctvb各劇場，咪撚再睇愛回家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我有預感cctvb股價會跌破新低，收視愈黎愈底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7357ecd3e7e69fc2b8b02a385979e06d67b69f","tid":1252153,"uid":6181,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T00:17:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9563d1f3134b010c570550b62b4b5e358d2e4658","tid":1252153,"uid":42217,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T00:17:28.000Z","msg":"所以佢先有500萬支持者"},{"pid":"5c583e7c5eb45f70f6443bb96a444cfeb3b74a8b","tid":1252153,"uid":6181,"like":297,"dislike":3,"score":294,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T00:21:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D0i3OBQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD0i3OBQ.png&h=7565d673&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96b44f04cd7dc284f99b364b18a2245c7a858435","tid":1252153,"uid":6181,"like":255,"dislike":